{"tid":651780,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"羅馬會長炮轟球證 「歐聯無VAR是笑話」","createTime":"2018-05-03T10:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T16:48:57.000Z","uid":160094,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"908d928f5e25e5c93ecd76efa5a2a9a54210e787","tid":651780,"uid":160094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fKIVtYvIx5M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfKIVtYvIx5M&d=7EB62gZsKTrwMWa9SY97DNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=76305284\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fKIVtYvIx5M</a><br />\n<br />\n羅馬周三晚雖然在歐聯準決賽次回合主場擊敗利物浦4:2，但兩回合計仍然輸6:7無緣決賽，羅馬會長柏洛達在賽後炮轟執法球證的水準，又謂如果歐聯仍不引入視像裁判系統（VAR），將會是一個大笑話。<br />\n<br />\n柏洛達賽後直言，歐聯絕對需要引入VAR，因為比賽根本不應該容許不公平的事情發生。他說：「49分鐘，艾沙拉維沒有越位，他完全是被門將撲跌。63分鐘的手球，也許全世界的人都看到了，就只有在場上的人看不到。67分鐘，柏德列舒希克也在禁區內被侵犯。我知道這樣的比賽是很難執法的，但我們這樣子在總比數落敗，真的令人非常難堪。話說回來，63分鐘所發生的事，也應該是紅牌，這樣會使對手只得十人應戰。利物浦是支很偉大的球隊，恭喜他們晉級，但如果歐聯沒有VAR，那根本是個笑話。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有VAR羅馬都一樣有紅牌同輸12碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeddc44a368e2658b5ae8ef5cf0bf57045707f51","tid":651780,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"利狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b78d8c66a29393786147ff698540cccb7fe5952","tid":651780,"uid":23815,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"佢收尾都幾君子<br />\n純粹覺得唔抵"},{"pid":"5c72cfc79b91eee193a069f44c679cd7bf44aa08","tid":651780,"uid":119450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:18:52.000Z","msg":"尋日羅馬都有手球啵..."},{"pid":"0b3cbca6fb833f3a2caf55499e8ffdb5bcc01667","tid":651780,"uid":581,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"Roma director of football Monchi says if VAR was being used